Dune - Greek Translation (Unofficial)
Author: Spyridon Papakotsis
Version: 1.0

This program will translate your Hard Disk installed "Dune" by Cryo, to Greek.

Supported versions are:
The original English, French, German and Italian releases.
IPF Numbers: #1156, #2393, #459, #2594.

You can easily apply this translation by double clicking the "Install_Translation" icon and following the installer's instructions. Help is available for every step.

This requires the "Installer" program to be in the Path.
If you don't have it, you can look for it in the WB3.0/3.1 "Install"
disk, or preferably download Installer-43.3.lha from Aminet.

WORKBENCH 1.x users should use the Install_for_WB13 script to apply the translation.

Alternatively, you can use the command line tool in the following
manner: dune_gr <Path to game drawer>

